@node REQUIREMENTS "Requirements"

To run Universal SID Scope (USS) requires you need at least
AmigaOS 3.0, MC68020 and MUI.

You also need SID player using playsid.library. Should work with
@{b}all@{ub} SID players using playsid.library but I have tested only
with HippoPlayer. Should work with the MagiC64 emulator, too.
@endnode
@node HISTORY "History of Universal SID Scope"

Version 1.3 (27th Feb 2002):
----------------------------

