Version 1.1 (9th May 2000):
---------------------------

        · Optimized code; CPU usage is significantly improved
        · Fixed redraw bug in the simple refresh mode
        · Added a tooltype: PRIORITY (controls task priority)

Version 1.0 (27th Feb 2000):
